eu.europa.esig.dss.x509.crl

Class OfflineCRLSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.europa.esig.dss.x509.crl.OfflineCRLSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CRLSource, RevocationSource<CRLToken>, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CAdESCRLSource, ExternalResourcesCRLSource, ListCRLSource, PAdESCRLSource, XAdESCRLSource

    public abstract class OfflineCRLSource
extends Object
implements CRLSource
    This class if a basic skeleton that is able to retrieve needed CRL data from the contained list. The child need to retrieve the list of wrapped CRLs.

    • Field Detail

      • crlsMap

        protected Map<String,byte[]> crlsMap
        This HashMap contains not validated CRL binaries. When the validation passes, the entry will be removed. The key is the SHA256 digest of the CRL binaries.
